<SecondaryPreamble>
<EnactingText>
<Para>
<Text>The Scottish Ministers, in exercise of the powers conferred by section 6(1) of the Fur Farming Prohibition (Scotland) Act 2002<FootnoteRef Ref="f00001"/>, hereby make the following Order:</Text>
</Para>
